    "subtype": "vehicle",
    "text": "Crafted by the wizard Vonthos as part of his bid to attempt the Test of the Starstone in Absalom, this strange vehicle is considered to be a magical and technological marvel. Vonthos's Golden Bridge is a flying sphere made out of a throne surrounded by several clockwork rings covered in gold and gems infused with powerful adaptive abjurations that grant it unique abilities.",
